<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">No. They are stand alone. However it was neat while reading book 2 and 3 and the references to the house and who used to live there thru the years. I <a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">No. They are stand alone. However it was neat while reading book 2 and 3 and the references to the house and who used to live there thru the years. I do recommend reading the other ones! <a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
