<span id="freeTextContainer6997492156932390368">Another bomb from Shreve. Her husband had a secret life...blah blah blah. She can&apos;t confront her grief and betrayal over finding this out, because he is dead. Then the usual fairy-tale ending for books of this genre...while Kathryn is grief-stricken, unkempt and unshowered and at her blubbery worst, a gorgeous guy is right there to fall madly in love with her! Yes, this happens *all* the time!</span>
