      <div class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/work/quotes/3131254-the-pilot-s-wife">Quotes from The Pilot&#39;s Wife</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
          <div class="stacked" tyle="padding-bottom:15px">
            <span class="readable">&ldquo;To leave, after all, was not the same as being left.&rdquo;</span>
            <nobr>
              &mdash;
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/quotes/264700-to-leave-after-all-was-not-the-same-as-being">259 likes</a>
            </nobr>
            <div class="clear"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="stacked" tyle="padding-bottom:15px">
            <span class="readable">&ldquo;Sometimes, she thought, courage was simply a matter of putting one foot in front of another and not stopping.&rdquo;</span>
